tesla,2026-02,324000,1279000,1240630,1470850,275400,405000,1.0,1,1,1,"Tesla's own Cumulative Paid Robotaxi Miles chart: monthly values vector-extracted from the Q4-2025 and Q1-2026 update-deck PDFs (overlapping months agree within ~3k mi; 658k end-2025, 1.717M end-Mar-2026). Texas driverless service only — the Q3-2025 call tracks Bay Area as a separate supervised series (1M+ mi by Oct 2025) and Aug-2025's ~13k delta is too small to contain the Bay fleet. Read as fleet service miles incl. deadhead, matching the incident scope (None + In-Vehicle Commercial/Test); if 'paid' is literally passenger-on-board miles the true total is higher, so kyoom_max carries ~15% upside and kyoom_min ~3% read noise."
